premise_source_doc_sentence: There are also several large hotels , including Hotell Järvsöbaden , Hotell Järvsö and Kramsta Gästgård & Konferens , the only hotel in the region that belongs to the large conference organization Svenska Möten  (  Swedish Meetings  )  .

In 1976 they produced a series of three short films for television about Agaton Sax , and also Agaton Sax and the Byköpings Village Festival , the first full-length entirely animated Swedish film , co-produced by the Swedish Film Institute .

Team Film also produced a series for small children , Totte  (  1973  )  , based on books by Gunilla Wolde , and three shorts based on other children 's books , Kattresan  (  1982  )  , Sjörövarfilmen  (  1983  )  , and Musikbussen  (  1994  )  , the first two again sponsored by the Swedish Film Institute .
The 49th Guldbagge Awards ceremony , presented by the Swedish Film Institute , honored the best Swedish films of 2013 and took place January 20 , 2014 , at Cirkus in Stockholm .
Daniel Bergman  (  born 1962  )  , Swedish film director
